# Instagram Reels Generator App Rules

## Core Principles
- Always follow React best practices and hooks conventions
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Implement proper error handling for all API calls
- Follow clean architecture patterns

## Technology Stack
- Frontend: React with TypeScript
- Backend: Node.js with Express
- Database: PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- Video Generation: RunwayML API
- Social Media: Instagram Graph API

## File Structure
- Components go in /components folder
- API routes in /api folder
- Utils and helpers in /utils folder
- Types in /types folder

## API Integration Guidelines
- Always use environment variables for API keys
- Implement proper error handling and retry logic
- Use async/await for all API calls
- Add request/response logging for debugging
